data.description:
PRICED TO SELL! Fantastic Opportunity in Willow Creek walking distance to Willow Creek Elementary and feeding into Cherry Creek High School! Located within walking distance to public transportation, Willow Creek Park, community pool, tennis courts, and a variety of local amenities including shops, restaurants, coffee shops, grocery stores, yoga and gym, this home is perfectly situated for a vibrant lifestyle.  

As you enter you will be wowed by the natural light! The living space is a great place for entertaining! The updated kitchen features newer soft close cabinets, quartz counters, & stainless steel appliances creating a stylish & functional space for culinary enthusiasts. Warm up by the fireplace and enjoy a nice meal or play games! Sliding glass doors from the kitchen open onto a south-facing deck inviting abundant natural light and seamless indoor-outdoor living. The backyard provides ample space for gardening and outdoor enjoyment.
With 4 beds up and 3 baths total along with finished basement with a FULL BATH ROUGH IN this home has it all! The basement is a great space for a theatre room, gaming room, rec room or add another bath and create a 5th bedroom suite. 

In addition the home offers fabulous primary living with oversized primary bedroom suite with room for den/office, 2 closets and a remodeled shower with custom tile! In addition to the fabulous primary there are bedrooms #2, #3 and #4 upstairs with updated bathroom! 

Builder George Writer believed in building communities that included parks, open space, and diverse housing types.  He was honored as Colorado Builder of the Year and his home are known quality and design.  
Willow Creek Elementary has won the prestigious National Blue Ribbon School of Excellence Award multiple times. In addition, it has won the John Irwin Schools of Excellence Award annually since 2001.  That award goes to the top eight percent of Colorado schools based on student achievement scores.
